{"word":"G618 - ἀπολαμβάνω - apolambánō - ap-ol-am-ban'-o - Receive","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπολαμβάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apolambánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ol-am-ban'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Receive</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அழை, வந்துசேர், அடை"},{"paragraph":"1. to receive"},{"paragraph":"2. to take again or back, to recover"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G2983 - λαμβάνω - lambánō - lam-ban'-o/2983\">G2983</a>; to <i>receive</i> (specifically in <i>full</i>, or as a host); also to <i>take aside:</i> - receive, take.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}